description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;A fantastic opportunity to join the Swansea Bay University Health Board Finance Team based in Headquarters in Baglan.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;This is an exciting opportunity to join the Swansea Bay University Health Board Finance Team. As a member of the team responsible in the provision of an effective and efficient workforce information service by monitoring and maintaining the quality of information held on the ESR system.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The successful candidate will assist with system queries on a day to day basis and provide a helpdesk service to ESR users.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The post holder will assist in checking all professional registration details ensure registration is current in line with Re-Registration Policy.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The post holder will provide administrative support to the Workforce Information Systems Manager.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The post holder will work as part of a team to ensure the new Swansea Bay University Health Board Finance Team are continuingly improving by identifying areas of improvement and supporting the team in taking forward projects linked to these improvements. These improvements include the on-going development of utilising technology to enhance the existing processes and building relationships with key stakeholders through influence. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Closing Date: 5th November 2020&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Should you have any queries relating to this post, please contact &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Leeann Gardner&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Workforce Information Systems Manager&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt; via email Leeann.Gardner@wales.nhs.uk&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
